channel.title: Login Fix?
channel.description:
Okay, so I compile, then run.
I go on moparscape, try to login to test it out...
Your account is already logged in. Try again later, or make another name.
On the running BAT file, it says:
[code]hyphen has joined the game <192.168.1.1> hyphen:error writing file hyphen: error writing file _ disconnected [/code]
Does anyone know how to solve this?
